## How to get the video:

### Fastest - Stock Video:
1. Visit: https://www.pexels.com/search/videos/jewellery/
2. Download a beautiful jewellery video
3. Save as: `jewellery-hero.mp4`
4. Put in this folder: `/public/videos/`

### Free - Create Your Own:
1. Record your jewellery products with phone
2. Use free video editor (CapCut, InShot)
3. Add elegant transitions
4. Export as MP4 (1920x1080)
5. Save as: `jewellery-hero.mp4`

### Professional - Hire Someone:
1. Find local videographer
2. Professional product photography
3. High-quality editing
4. Brand integration

